
For installation instruction, read the INSTALL file.

To run the server, just type as root:
	#/> mlvmd
If you want to start an imago, you can either use the command line client (ugly) or us the gui interface provided with this distribution.
To use the command line client type:
	$/> mlvmc

Then, you can load imago file with the LOAD commandand providing the full path to the compiled file.
Example:
	LOAD /path/to/file/imago.lo

You can run the server as root and the client as simple user without any security issues.

For more info, after installation, run the manual pages.

